title: Boykin helps No. 2 TCU rally past Kansas State, 52-45 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,191 Boykin helps No. 2 TCU rally past Kansas State, 52-45 (Yahoo Sports) MANHATTAN, Kan. (AP) -- Trevone Boykin threw for 301 yards and two touchdowns, the second a 55-yard strike to Josh Doctson with 1:10 left in the game, and second-ranked TCU rallied from a big halftime deficit to beat Kansas State 52-45 on Saturday night.
